<br>
Ok NOTHING on a computer currently is a RPG.<br>
<br>
As someone who has designed tabletop Role Playing Games (real RPGs) and who was involved in the industry for a long time... I take GREAT offense to you thinking that anything on a computer currently comes close to a good RPG.<br>
<br>
Please, call them adventure games or action games or (as I like to call them) Chain of Events Puzzle Games.<br>
<br>
But please don't call them RPGs, that's insulting to the people who make real RPGs. <p><center>Nakath Thunderbush<BR>
Janitor<BR>
<a href=http://pub37.ezboard.com/bresolutionforums>Resolution</a><BR>
